dreaming machine ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; yume &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is an unfinished japanese anime fantasy-adventure film by satoshi kon . it would have been the director 's fifth feature film . after kon 's death on august 24 , 2010 , production continued at madhouse , where the team used satoshi kon 's directorial tapes and notes to guide them to completing the film , though the main work such as storyboards and script was already complete . in august 2011 , madhouse founder &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; revealed that production of the film had been halted due to lack of finances . only 600 of 1,500 shots have been animated . however , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; still intends to finish the film , however long it takes .